    "form_header_text": "FY27 IL-08 Programmatic or Report Language Appropriations Request Form",
    "form_instructions_text": "Please fill out the below form to request that Congressman Krishnamoorthi submit a specific fiscal year 2027 (FY27) Programmatic or Report Language appropriations request. If you would like him to submit an original request, which is a request with no current lead sponsor, please contact Anna Dodge, our Legislative Director, at Anna.Dodge@mail.house.gov. A form for Community Project Funding will be available once guidance is published from the Approporiations Committee. Please note that filling out this form does not guarantee the Congressman will sign on to the appropriations request submitted. \n\nThe House Appropriations Committee has not published guidance for the FY27 appropriations cycle.  Please see the following link for the FY26 appropriations cycle guidance, we do not anticipate significant changes for FY27: https://appropriations.house.gov/fy26-member-requests/fy26-guidance-overview.  Please review this guidance before submitting an application.  We will update the form as new guidance becomes available.\n\nPlease have ALL FY27 Programmatic/Language requests submitted by March 6th. Thank you!\n\nIf you have any further questions, please call Congressman Krishnamoorthi's office at (202) 225-3711.",
